{"componentChunkName":"component---src-markdown-template-js","path":"/v1.0/utilities/margin","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>마진 (margin)</h1>\n<p>클래스 입력을 통해 마진값을 손쉽게 넣어줄 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>모든 margin</h2>\n<p>상하좌우 <code class=\"language-text\">rem</code> 값을 기준으로 마진을 넣어줄 때 사용합니다.</p>\n<p>기본적으로 0~10 까지 입력 가능합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"show-col mg-2\">\nmg-2\n</div>\n<div class=\"show-col mg-4\">\nmg-4\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>mg-2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> mg-2 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>mg-4<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> mg-4 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n<h2>상하, 좌우 margin</h2>\n<p>상하(위, 아래) 또는 좌우(왼쪽, 오른쪽) <code class=\"language-text\">rem</code> 값을 기준으로 마진을 넣어줄 때 사용합니다.</p>\n<p>기본적으로 0~10 까지 입력 가능합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"show-col mg-tb-2\">mg-tb-2</div>\n<div class=\"show-col mg-lr-4\"